-- Nigerian forex reserves down 2.6 pct month-on-month to $37.14 bln 
-- By Oludare Mayowa
-- Fri May 30, 2014 10:09AM EDT
-- None



LAGOS, May 30 (Reuters) - Nigerian foreign exchange reserves declined 2.62 percent month-on-month to $37.14 billion by May 27, from $38.14 billion a month earlier, latest data from the central bank showed on Friday.

